python manage.py startapp genre


Python web project create
=============================

Step1: django-admin startproject codedaddies_list ---- create django project from django admin.
Step2: django-admin startapp my_app               ---- create app in django project
Step3: python manage.py migrate                   ---- arrange new started project
Step4: python manage.py createsuperuser           ---- create super
Step5: python manage.py makemigrations, python manage.py migrate            ---- after created every model

Note:  
 
  -  Register every model which is created by models.py in admin.py.
  -  Mention every app newly created in settings.py under INSTALLED_APPS

